'''Anthropologie''' ye donni yé mi be tali kè [[adamadéya]] kan. A be adamadé kalan a fan bè ladjèléfè. Djekouloubola, sigiyorobola, kètiokoyabola, kokètiokoyaw ani takabolo. Ale kalanbolo sinssinibè mokow kètiokoyala djekouloukono, djekouloul minou tè djekoulou baw ye. [[Ethnologie]] oye ka siyaw kalan, anthropologie oye ka adamadé yèrède kalan, kalantiokobèladjèla.

Takabolo caman be anthropologila, minou nafakabo kosèbè olouye [[sociologie|sociologikalanso]] mi bè fransikawfè ye ([[Emile Durkheim]], [[Marcel Mauss]], [[Claude Levi-Strauss]]), anthropologie mibè djekoukouwkan Anglaiwfè ye ([[James George Frazer|J.G. Frazer]]), [[Bronislaw Malinoski]], [[Alfred Reginal Radcliffe-Brown|A.R. Radcliffe-Brown]], [[Edward Evan Evans-Pritchard|E.E. Evans-Pritchard]], a ni anthropologie mibè kokètiokoyawkan Amerikawfè ye ([[Lewis Henry Morgan|L.H. Morgan]], [[Franz Boas]], [[Marvin Harris]], [[Clifford Geertz]]).

